## msi-parent

**Value type:** `<phandle>` or `<prop-encoded-array>`

A phandle (with optional MSI specifier cells) to the MSI controller for the device. Specifies which MSI controller handles MSI/MSI-X interrupts for this device.

```dts
/* arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/sm8550.dtsi */
pcie0: pci@1c00000 {
    compatible = "qcom,pcie-sm8550";
    msi-parent = <&pcie0_msi>;
};
```
